Menu Eleven Reloaded
====================

Maintainer
----------

dshep79 maintains this Menu Eleven Reloaded fork.

Upstream projects
-----------------

The immediate upstream project is MenuEleven/Cinnamenu11, created by
David Banting:
https://github.com/ForsetGump1952/Cinnamenu11

That project is itself based on Cinnamenu, originally created by Jason Hicks:
https://github.com/jaszhix/Cinnamenu

David Banting updated the Cinnamon 5.8-era applet with a Windows 11-inspired
layout, configurable theme spacing, and a mixed view for pinned applications
and recent files. This Reloaded package keeps those credits intact, uses an
independent UUID, and includes packaging and security hygiene changes.

Fork artwork
------------

The white applet icon is an original generic menu mark made specifically for
this fork. Branded search-provider logos have been removed. Search,
calculator, and Wikipedia results use generic symbolic icons supplied by the
desktop icon theme.

search.py taken from placesCenter@scollins cinnamon applet https://github.com/linuxmint/cinnamon-spices-applets/tree/master/placesCenter%40scollins

Additional keywords in emoji.js are from emojilib (https://github.com/muan/emojilib) License: MIT

Web search suggestions provided by DuckDuckGo.

